13 April 2021 The Government Communication and Information System in partnership with the National Press Club and the Department of Science and Innovation will host a webinar to look at the future alternative energy sources. Members of the media are invited to attend a virtual webinar. Details are as follows: Date:  Wednesday, 14 April 2021Time:  10h00 – 11h30Platform: Zoom (Webinar ID 935 1126 9742 Passcode 248090) Panellist: Rebecca Maserumule, Chief Director Hydrogen and Energy: Department of Science and Innovation Knox Msebenzi, Managing Director: Nuclear Industry of South Africa Media participation: Journalists may view the webinar via live streaming on the following social media links below: Facebook:    http://facebook.com/GovernmentZA Twitter:         http://twitter.com/dsigovza http://twitter.com/GovernmentZA YouTube:     https://www.youtube.com/user/GovernmentZA RSVP to Ignicious Masilela on Email: Ignicious@gcis.gov.za Enquiries:William BaloyiCell: 083 390 7147